These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, lemonade, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, pilot, firefighter, electrician
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the firefighter##1
2. the electrician is on the far left##1
3. the firefighter is between the pilot and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | water         | juice   | lemonade | cola       |
| Job      | electrician | teacher | firefighter   | pilot |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
4 different pets are kept: horse, goldfish, rabbit, rat
1. the owner of the rat is between the person who's hobby is reading and the owner of the goldfish##2
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | gardening | reading | video-games |
| Pet   | goldfish    | rat   | horse | rabbit       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, salsa, rock, gospel
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, british, colombian, french
1. the colombian is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
2. the colombian is between the british and the fan of salsa##2
3. the british is on the far left##1
4. the french is on the left of the fan of rock##1
5. the fan of salsa is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre          | gospel    | r&b | salsa   | rock  |
| Nationality   | british | colombian   | french | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, house, gospel, pop
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon, rugby, tennis
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is the fan of house##1
2. the fan of jazz is between the person who's sport is basketball and the fan of pop##2
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
4. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Music-Genre     | pop   | jazz    | gospel       | house   |
| Sport   | rugby | tennis | basketball | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, soy-milk
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, rabbit, snake
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is between the owner of the dog and the owner of the frog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Beverage   | fanta        | iced-tea | soy-milk  | hot-chocolate |
| Pet      | rabbit | frog  | snake | dog    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, d&b, pop, salsa
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, ritmeester, prince, aristoff
1. the prince-smoker is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
2. the fan of salsa is the prince-smoker##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
4. the fan of d&b is the havana-smoker##1
5. the fan of pop is between the fan of classical and the fan of d&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | pop           | classical | salsa  |
| Cigar         | havana | aristoff | ritmeester   | prince |

