.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, cola, water, fanta
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, roller, snowmobile
1. the person drinking cola is the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person driving the bus and the person drinking water##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | fanta   | cola | soy-milk | water      |
| Transport     | roller | bus    | motorbike  | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, lily, bellflower, orchid
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, snowmobile
1. the person driving the helicopter is the person who growslily##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is between the person who growsbellflower and the person driving the roller##2
3. the person who growsazalea is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Flower       | azalea | orchid | bellflower     | lily   |
| Transport   | roller   | motorbike     | snowmobile | helicopter |

