.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, entrepreneur, librarian, videographer
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, orange, yellow, white
1. the librarian is between the person who likes apricot and the dressmaker##2
2. the person who likes white is on the left of the dressmaker##1
3. the videographer is on the right of the dressmaker##1
4. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes white##1
5. the dressmaker is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | entrepreneur | librarian | dressmaker | videographer |
| Color   | apricot         | white       | orange    | yellow         |

