.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, garlic, peach, plum
4 different games are played: scrabble, billiard, go, snooker
1. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person eating plum##1
2. the person playing go is on the right of the person eating peach##1
3. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
4. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
5. the person playing billiard is between the person eating garlic and the person playing snooker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | plum   | peach      | garlic   | avocado  |
| Game   | snooker | billiard | go | scrabble |

