.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
City: edinburgh, venice, prague, miami
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, pop, punk, trance
1. the fan of punk is the person traveling to venice##1
2. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of trance##1
3. the fan of gospel is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
4. the person traveling to prague is the fan of pop##1
5. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
6. the fan of pop is between the person traveling to venice and the person traveling to miami##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| City         | venice | prague | miami | edinburgh |
| Music-Genre   | punk          | pop     | trance  | gospel     |

