.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-13::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, backgammon, billiard, mah-jongg
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, documentary, sports
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person watching sports movies and the person playing scrabble##2
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
4. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Game           | scrabble | mah-jongg | backgammon | billiard     |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | documentary    | sports   | adventure |

