.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, subway, van, snowmobile
4 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, lizard, rabbit
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is the owner of the lizard##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the goat and the person driving the subway##2
4. the owner of the rabbit is the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Transport   | snowmobile | subway | jet-ski | van |
| Pet           | lizard  | rabbit  | goldfish | goat      |

