.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-18::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
4 different games are played: snooker, whist, go, bridge
1. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person playing snooker and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person playing snooker##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby       | singing | puzzles | rock-climbing | collecting |
| Game   | snooker    | whist  | bridge    | go       |

