.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, scooter, quad-bike, jet-ski
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, golf, rowing
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person driving the trike and the person driving the quad-bike##2
5. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Transport   | jet-ski   | trike   | scooter | quad-bike |
| Sport         | baseball | basketball | rowing     | golf    |

