.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
House: townhouse, craftsman, cape-cod, cottage
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1
2. the townhouse house is between the owner of the cat and the cottage house##2
3. the cottage house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
4. the craftsman house is on the far right##1
5. the craftsman house is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| House   | cape-cod    | cottage     | townhouse | craftsman |
| Pet     | chinchilla | guinea-pig | goat       | cat     |

 